            <div class='post' itemprop='articleBody'>
              <p>It would be great to set an account-wide default color palette. The existing defaults include a very very light cyan that is super difficult to read.</p>
<p>A default color palette would allow brand colors to be established and used in every visualization without having to over-ride with hex codes.</p>
<p>Also, if the nature of the data being visualized means the number of series changes over time, this would allow the overall visualization to not look disjointed if this occurs.</p>
            </div>

