            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>Would love to see this as part of the front-end. If you feel like hacking on your instance, you can modify the default color scheme with <a href="https://github.com/getredash/redash/blob/master/client/app/visualizations/ColorPalette.js">this file</a>. Then rebuild your front-end assets and you’re good to go!</p>
            </div>

