            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>seems like the location of the file changed to <a href="https://github.com/getredash/redash/blob/master/viz-lib/src/visualizations/ColorPalette.js" rel="nofollow noopener">here</a></p>
<p>+1 on some sort of color palette management options; would be great if I could predefine a number of palettes and then choose between them in the different viz types depending on what suits the data. while researching the topic I found this <a href="https://gka.github.io/chroma.js/" rel="nofollow noopener">https://gka.github.io/chroma.js/</a> which looks potentially helpful if one wanted ways to generate palettes straight in redash (which would be even more awesome).</p>
            </div>

